  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">How Much Does Basement Waterproofing Cost in Milton?</h2>

        <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 p-6 mb-8 speakable">
          <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
            Basement waterproofing in Milton costs $145–$280 per linear foot for exterior systems, with most homes totaling $13,000–$27,000. Milton homeowners can access Halton Region basement flooding protection programs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg  max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
