              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
                <span class="font-bold">Typical Solution:</span> Full exterior excavation, foundation repair, modern weeping tile, sump pump installation.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-cyan-600">
