                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 uppercase">First Boom</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
                <span class="font-bold">Characteristics:</span> First major suburban expansion, Dempsey/Willmott areas, builder-grade waterproofing, mixed quality.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
                <span class="font-bold">Common Issues:</span> Builder-grade membrane failures, inadequate drainage design, grading settlement, sump overwhelm.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
                <span class="font-bold">Typical Solution:</span> Exterior membrane replacement, enhanced drainage, sump capacity upgrade, backwater valve.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-cyan-600">
                Avg Cost: $15,000–$25,000
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Era 3: 2000s-2010s -->
          <div class="border-2 border-slate-200 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-cyan-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                3
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">2000s-2010s</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 uppercase">Hyper Growth</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
