              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
                <span class="font-bold">Common Issues:</span> Rushed construction settling, overwhelmed storm systems, slope drainage failures, Tarion warranty claims.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
                <span class="font-bold">Typical Solution:</span> Post-construction upgrades, independent drainage, enhanced sump systems, slope stabilization.
